item.title: gophercon sg 2017 reflection
item.description: This is first time attending a conference outside my country. It was pretty exciting and scary because I’m going alone but nonetheless it was an amazing experience. I met a couple of interesting people and mostly I think it boost more my confidence in travelling. The first day was all about learning Go for Intermediate developers by William Kennedy. I learned quite a lot, although I’ve been using Go in work for some time now, I admit that I still have a long way to go.
